records.addlTxt:
The State files an Amended Information which amend the charge to operate without owners consent-joyriding, contrary to Section 943.23(3m) of the Wisconsin Statutes.
NO CONTEST plea entered to the amended charge.  Convicted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for twelve (12) months.
Conditions of probation:
1) AODA assessment and follow through;
2) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
3) Maintain fulltime employment, schooling or work search;
4) Pay court costs of $671.03;
5) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Minutes.
